Class ProxyMapCache<T extends SonarObject>

java.lang.Object
us.mn.state.dot.tms.client.proxy.ProxyMapCache<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<MapGeoLoc>
public final class ProxyMapCache<T extends SonarObject> extends Object implements Iterable<MapGeoLoc>
A cache mapping from MapGeoLoc to proxy objects. This cache is an optimization to help ProxyManager.findProxy run fast.
Author:
Douglas Lau
